entries.title: Nvidia may have another monster GPU in the works, and the price could be outrageous
entries.description: It seems that Nvidia is really preparing a Titan RTX 40-series GPU. The specs of the card just popped up in a shipping manifest.

entries.title: Tested: Is Discord really slowing down Nvidia GPUs?
entries.description: If you're using Discord, be aware that a recent update may have impacted the performance of your Nvidia GPU -- but is it a big deal?
